About Us
A Warm Welcome to Destiny RV Park
At Destiny RV Park, we pride ourselves on creating a peaceful and friendly environment for travelers and residents alike. Nestled in the heart of Florida, our 55+ community is designed to offer a perfect balance of relaxation and convenience. With live-on-site managers, full-hookup RV sites, and proximity to local attractions, we’re committed to making every guest feel at home.
Experience the Best of Florida Living
Our prime location near Bushnell, FL, puts you within reach of historic landmarks, bustling markets, and natural beauty. Whether you’re exploring the Florida National Cemetery or enjoying the lively Webster Flea Market, there’s something for everyone to enjoy just minutes away. Our community is also convenient to everyday essentials, including shopping, dining, and medical facilities.
Comfort and Convenience at Every Turn
Destiny RV Park offers a range of amenities to enhance your stay, including paved roads, street lighting, laundry facilities, and a serene pond. All sites feature full hookups with electric, water, and waste, and many include covered parking options. With quiet surroundings, pet-friendly policies, and a welcoming atmosphere, you’ll find everything you need for a relaxing and enjoyable experience.
